  "title": "WAREHOUSE ASSISTANT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Descriptions:</strong></p><ol><li>Assist Manager to perform warehousing and logistics daily operations.</li><li>Oversees all inbound and outbound activities, warehouse operations and Organisation</li><li>Report on any stock discrepancies</li><li>Setup layout and ensure efficient space utilisation</li><li>Conduct stock take periodically</li><li>Liaise with relevant departments on daily operations.</li><li>Other duties as assigned by management</li></ol><p>Requirements :</p><ul><li>Supervising warehouse staff and daily activities.</li><li>Managing, evaluating and reporting on warehouse productivity.</li><li>Tracking and coordinating the receipt, storage, and timely delivery of goods and materials.</li><li>Ordering supplies and maintaining suitable inventory levels.</li><li>Checking orders, bills, items received, inventory, and deliveries for accuracy.</li><li>Maintaining records, reporting relevant information, and preparing any necessary documentation.</li><li>Ensuring basic maintenance standards and compliance with health and safety regulations.</li><li>Performing a daily inspection of the warehouse grounds.</li><li>Coordinating and maintaining fleets and equipment.</li><li>Communicating and coordinating with other departments and customers.</li><li>Ability to meet deadlines.</li><li>Good interpersonal & communication skills</li><li>Ability to work in a fast-paced and dynamic environment</li><li>Physically fit and able to handle heavy load goods</li></ul>",
